      <description><![CDATA[
<b>New:</b>
<ul>
<li>Brand logos for the Cline, jcode, MiMo Code, and gjc tabs, instead of a letter badge.</li>
</ul>
<b>Improved:</b>
<ul>
<li>The client-tab row now scrolls with a plain vertical mouse wheel, so a mouse without a horizontal-scroll wheel can reach every tab.</li>
</ul>
<b>Fixes:</b>
<ul>
<li>Antigravity CLI now shows the shared Antigravity quota instead of an empty or duplicate limit card.</li>
</ul>
